									<div class="">
										<h4 class="font-bold">About</h4>
										<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
											<p class="whitespace-normal mr-4">
												I made a special dropdown for the new PIN App using React Native and Expo.
												It's easy to search and you can even make your own filters. I did this project in my free time to show my skills and expand my portfolio.
												It's a good example of how I make simple and helpful software.
											</p>
