											</div>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>


						<div class="relative bg-white drop-shadow-lg rounded-xl p-4 mt-8">
							<img class="absolute bg-white rounded-full drop-shadow p-2 w-12 -left-4 -top-4 z-0" src="/puck/puck-4.png" />
							<div class="z-10 mt-4">
								<div class="flex flex-row">
									<h3 class="text-xl font-bold border-b pr-4">PIN (Pay It Now) Mobile App</h3>
									<div class="flex flex-row ml-auto gap-2">
										<a class="px-4 py-1 drop-shadow bg-white rounded-xl text-center my-auto font-bold uppercase" href="https://payitnow.io/download-app/" target="_blank">
											Download
										</a>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="max-w-3/4 mt-3">
									<h4 class="font-bold">About</h4>
									<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
										<p class="whitespace-normal mr-4">
											As one of the current maintainer and developer of the PIN Network App,
											I am responsible for both its ongoing upkeep and the development of its new version.
											The PIN Network mobile application serves as the primary interface for interacting with the network,
											offering users a range of essential features such as payment options, reward opportunities,
											and digital wallet management. As a dedicated and skilled developer,
											I am committed to ensuring the app provides a seamless and user-friendly experience for all users of the PIN Network.
										</p>
										<img class="rounded-xl border w-full md:w-2/5 md:h-1/2 md:my-auto" src="/projects/payitnow-app-hero.avif" />
									</div>
									<div class="mt-3">
										<h4 class="font-bold">Technologies</h4>
										<div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
											<div class="p-2 drop-shadow bg-white rounded-xl flex-row flex items-center">
												<img class="w-8" src="/software/react-icon.svg" />
												<h5 class="font-bold text-md ml-2">React Native</h5>
